WEBVTT

00:12.880 --> 00:16.083
‐‐ Captions by VITAC ‐‐
www.vitac.com

00:25.259 --> 00:26.927
<i>PREVIOUSLY ON WEEDS...</i>

00:26.960 --> 00:28.428
I THINK I'M YOUR SON.

00:28.462 --> 00:29.796
MOTHER OF SHIT.

00:29.830 --> 00:30.864
I WANT TO TAKE YOUR CLASS.

00:30.898 --> 00:33.734
WELCOME
TO APPLIED CRIMINAL JUSTICE.

00:33.767 --> 00:35.636
WHERE AM I GOING?
CUSTODY HEARING.

00:35.669 --> 00:36.503
STEVIE'S GONNA BE THERE.

00:36.537 --> 00:38.839
I WANT TO SEE MY SON.
LET ME IN, SCOTT.

00:38.872 --> 00:40.107
Jill: <i>DON'T TOUCH THE GATE,</i>
<i>SCOTT.</i>

00:40.140 --> 00:41.275
IT SUCKS. I GET IT.

00:41.308 --> 00:43.177
SO YOU'LL BACK ME?
SORRY.

00:43.210 --> 00:44.845
Silas: WENT THROUGH
SIX OR SEVEN VARIATIONS

00:44.878 --> 00:46.280
BEFORE I CAME UP
WITH THAT ONE.

00:46.313 --> 00:47.481
IS THAT RIGHT?

00:47.514 --> 00:49.550
THAT'S THAT MOTHER‐FUCKING
MILF WEED.

00:49.583 --> 00:51.485
TELL ME YOU HAVE GOOD NEWS
ABOUT OUR WEED SUPPLY.

00:51.518 --> 00:52.920
JILL HAS SCHEDULED
A CUSTODY HEARING.

00:52.953 --> 00:54.855
I NEED YOU TO COME
AND BE A CHARACTER WITNESS.

00:54.888 --> 00:56.223
MAYBE
WE SHOULD'VE CALLED FIRST.

00:56.256 --> 00:57.758
THEY GROW WEED.
WE HAVE MONEY. IT'LL BE FINE.

00:57.791 --> 00:59.526
I HOPE YOU'RE RIGHT.

00:59.560 --> 01:01.795
HELL NO.

01:01.828 --> 01:03.230
[ SHOTGUN COCKS ]

01:05.832 --> 01:07.234
MAYBE WE SHOULD RUN.
DON'T BE SILLY.

01:07.267 --> 01:08.735
[ GUNSHOT ]

01:08.769 --> 01:09.703
[ GRUNTS ]

01:09.736 --> 01:12.139
HEYLIA, YOU PSYCHO!

01:13.473 --> 01:14.942
PEEK OUT.

01:14.975 --> 01:15.943
YOU PEEK OUT.

01:15.976 --> 01:16.977
BE THE MAN.

01:17.010 --> 01:18.512
BE THE MOM.

01:18.545 --> 01:19.880
[ SIGHS ]

01:19.913 --> 01:23.817
HEYLIA, I'M COMING OUT.
PLEASE DON'T SHOOT.

01:23.851 --> 01:26.053
YEE‐HAW!
[ SHOTGUN COCKS ]

01:26.086 --> 01:27.721
[ GUNSHOT ]

01:28.822 --> 01:31.091
GLAD WE TOOK
THE EXTENDED COVERAGE.

01:31.124 --> 01:33.827
[ GUNSHOT ]
I GUESS
SHE DOES HOLD A GRUDGE.

01:33.861 --> 01:35.629
[ LAUGHS ]

01:37.764 --> 01:40.267
YOU WANT THE SHERIFF
OUT HERE?!

01:40.300 --> 01:43.837
YOU DID NOT JUST TAKE THE GUN
AWAY FROM THE BLACK WOMAN.

01:43.871 --> 01:44.805
WHAT ARE YOU
SHOOTING AT?

01:44.838 --> 01:46.473
THE FUCK?

01:46.507 --> 01:47.708
HI, DEAN.

01:47.741 --> 01:49.076
NANCY?

01:49.943 --> 01:51.812
CELIA ISN'T WITH YOU,
IS SHE?!

01:51.845 --> 01:53.480
NO.

01:53.514 --> 01:55.315
OH, STOP.

01:55.349 --> 01:56.850
SHIT.

01:56.884 --> 01:57.885
IT'S MY OWN DAMN FAULT.

01:57.918 --> 01:59.853
SHOULD HAVE DROPPED YOU
FIRST TIME

01:59.887 --> 02:02.523
YOU DROVE YOUR NARROW ASS
DOWN THE 110.

02:02.556 --> 02:05.792
THE SHIT YOUR SHIT'S BLOWN
ALL OVER MY SHIT!

02:05.826 --> 02:08.061
I PAID FOR MY SHIT ‐‐
IN FULL!

02:08.095 --> 02:10.030
SHE WENT TO PRISON.

02:10.063 --> 02:11.498
ANY GIRL‐ON‐GIRL
ACTION?

02:11.532 --> 02:12.799
I JUST WANT TO TALK.

02:12.833 --> 02:13.967
WE. WE WANT TO TALK.

02:14.001 --> 02:15.969
Heylia: FUCK A TALK ‐‐
YOU IN HUMBOLDT NOW,

02:16.003 --> 02:18.939
WHERE PROPERTY LAWS SAY
I CAN DEFEND MY LAND

02:18.972 --> 02:21.642
AGAINST ANY AND ALL AGGRESSORS,
TRESPASSERS,

02:21.675 --> 02:24.011
AND INTERLOPIN'
NIGHTMARE BITCHES FROM THE PAST.

02:24.044 --> 02:25.712
[ SHOTGUN COCKS ]

02:26.713 --> 02:29.883
NO OFFENSE, CHICKEN,
BUT COME ON.

02:29.917 --> 02:32.119
WE JUST WANT POT.
WE HAVE MONEY.

02:32.152 --> 02:34.955
I DON'T CARE IF YOU GOT A GOOSE
THAT SHITS GOLD NUGGETS.

02:34.988 --> 02:36.857
HOW YOU EVEN FIND OUT
WHERE I LIVE?

02:36.890 --> 02:39.159
IN COPENHAGEN,
I FOUND CONRAD ON FACEBOOK.

02:39.193 --> 02:41.028
HE ONLY HAD NINE FRIENDS.

02:41.061 --> 02:42.896
YEAH,
IS ‐‐ IS HE HERE?

02:42.930 --> 02:44.765
NONE OF
YOUR FUCKIN' BUSINESS.

02:44.798 --> 02:45.866
WHY ARE YOU HERE?

02:45.899 --> 02:48.001
IT'S A LONG STORY.
NO, IT AIN'T.

02:48.035 --> 02:49.136
IT'S KIND OF LONG.

02:49.169 --> 02:51.104
SHUT THE FUCK UP!

02:51.138 --> 02:54.074
WHERE THE HELL ARE WE?

02:55.275 --> 02:59.112
OH, YOU IN HEYLIA JAMES'
NEIGHBORHOOD.

03:00.547 --> 03:03.317
[ SAW WHIRRING ]

03:04.785 --> 03:08.789
YOU DIDN'T WANT TO
BE IN A POLYAMOROUS
RELATIONSHIP, ANYWAY ‐‐

03:08.822 --> 03:10.023
NOT WITH
DYING OLD CANCER GUY.

03:10.057 --> 03:12.192
YEAH,
IT WASN'T A POLY...

03:12.226 --> 03:16.063
OKAY, CHARLES MAY HAVE
CUPPED MY ASS ONCE.

03:16.096 --> 03:18.665
AND YOU DON'T WANT
TO BE TIED DOWN IN N. Y. C.,

03:18.699 --> 03:20.100
FUCK CENTER
OF THE UNIVERSE.

03:20.133 --> 03:22.469
I GOT BIGGER THINGS
ON MY MIND.

03:22.503 --> 03:25.239
CHARLES TOLD ME
TO PUT MY BALLS OUT THERE.

03:25.272 --> 03:28.509
WELL, HERE.
HERE'S MY BALLS.

03:28.542 --> 03:31.612
THE GOOFY ELECTRIC‐BIKE THING
YOU SOLD IN DENMARK?

03:31.645 --> 03:34.882
UH, NOT ONLY IS
THE COPENHAGEN WHEEL NOT GOOFY,

03:34.915 --> 03:36.650
SELLING IT MIGHT BE

03:36.683 --> 03:39.753
THE ONLY LEGITIMATE GOOD IDEA
I'VE EVER HAD IN MY LIFE.

03:39.786 --> 03:41.121
AM I RIGHT, SHANE?

03:41.154 --> 03:43.891
I'M NOT BANKROLLING YOUR
GOOFY ELECTRIC‐BIKE THING, ANDY.

03:43.924 --> 03:45.959
JERNS GAVE ME EXCLUSIVE RIGHTS
TO NEW YORK.

03:45.993 --> 03:48.061
I HAVE EXPERIENCE.
I EVEN FOUND A SPACE.

03:48.095 --> 03:51.798
I JUST NEED AN INITIAL INFLUX
OF $80,000 ‐‐

03:51.832 --> 03:53.033
NO.

03:53.066 --> 03:55.369
COME ON. GIVE ME
SOME OF YOUR FAKE COLLEGE LOANS.

03:55.402 --> 03:56.770
NO.

03:56.803 --> 03:57.804
GIVE ME SOME MONEY!

03:57.838 --> 03:58.939
[ CHUCKLES ]

03:58.972 --> 04:00.974
SHANE. GIVE ME MONEY.

04:01.008 --> 04:02.442
MONEY. MONEY.

04:02.476 --> 04:04.311
GIVE ME SOME MONEY, SHANE.
MONEY. MONEY.

04:04.344 --> 04:05.946
SHANE, QUIT BEING
A SELFISH PRICK!

04:05.979 --> 04:07.214
GIVE ME SOME MONEY.

04:07.247 --> 04:09.216
I'M SORRY THAT I CALLED YOU
"SELFISH" JUST THEN.

04:09.249 --> 04:10.751
NO.

04:10.784 --> 04:12.386
FUCK YOU!

04:12.419 --> 04:14.054
THIS IS A LOW.

04:15.222 --> 04:16.557
WELL, THE HEDGE FUND
DABBLES IN V. C.

04:16.590 --> 04:19.560
THEY'RE ALWAYS LOOKING
FOR SOME NEW BULLSHIT COMPANIES

04:19.593 --> 04:20.928
TO ADD
TO THE HOUSE OF CARDS.

04:20.961 --> 04:22.729
SERIOUSLY?
YEAH.
COME PITCH TO THE GUYS.

04:22.763 --> 04:25.599
I'LL MAKE WHIT SQUEEZE YOU IN.
THAT DUDE WORSHIPS ME.

04:25.632 --> 04:28.735
[ CHUCKLES ] I GOT TO TELL YOU,
IT'S REALLY REFRESHING.

04:28.769 --> 04:30.737
DOUG, THANKS!

04:30.771 --> 04:31.738
FUCKER!

04:31.772 --> 04:34.508
THAT'S AMAZING.
THANKS.

04:34.541 --> 04:35.976
OH, YEAH.

04:36.009 --> 04:37.878
[ SAW WHIRRING ]

04:37.911 --> 04:39.713
SLOW DOWN.

04:39.746 --> 04:41.215
I'M ON MY CHORES.

04:41.248 --> 04:44.151
YOU JUST SOMEONE FOLLOWING
SOMEONE FOR NO DAMN GOOD REASON.

04:44.184 --> 04:46.687
DON'T YOU WANT TO KNOW
WHY I WAS IN PRISON?

04:46.720 --> 04:47.921
INVOLUNTARY DUMBASSERY,

04:47.955 --> 04:50.524
FIRST‐DEGREE STEPPING‐IN‐SHIT‐
YOU‐CAN'T‐HANDLE.

04:50.557 --> 04:51.625
[ SIGHS ]

04:51.658 --> 04:53.126
WHERE'S CONRAD?

04:53.160 --> 04:56.029
ONCE A MONTH, HE DRIVES DOWN
TO L. A. TO SELL TO THE CLUBS.

04:56.063 --> 04:58.265
YOU KNOW WHAT I THOUGHT
WHEN YOU PULLED UP?

04:58.298 --> 05:00.667
THOUGHT SOME 5‐YEAR‐OLD
HALF‐COCOA CHILD

05:00.701 --> 05:04.538
WAS GONNA STEP OUT THE CAR
AND START CALLING ME "GRANDMA."

05:04.571 --> 05:07.174
[ CHUCKLES ]
THAT'S FUNNY.

05:07.207 --> 05:10.811
YOU WERE ALWAYS FUNNY.
I MISSED YOU.

05:10.844 --> 05:14.615
LeVAN USED TO HAVE
THIS STUFFED PENGUIN.

05:14.648 --> 05:15.883
HE'D LOSE IT.

05:15.916 --> 05:18.385
HOWL LIKE THE SKY
HAD JUST BEEN SNUFFED OUT.

05:18.418 --> 05:20.654
BUT THEN
HE'D SEE SOMETHING ELSE ‐‐

05:20.687 --> 05:22.155
DOG, MY EARRINGS,
WHATEVER ‐‐

05:22.189 --> 05:24.424
AND JUST LIKE THAT,
HE'D FORGET

05:24.458 --> 05:27.194
THE UNIVERSE EVER KNEW
A THING CALLED A PENGUIN.

05:28.161 --> 05:29.863
AM I LeVAN
IN THIS STORY?

05:29.897 --> 05:31.532
IT'S CALLED
OBJECT IMPERMANENCE.

05:31.565 --> 05:34.768
AND $1,000 SAY
MY BLACK ASS CROSSED YOUR MIND

05:34.801 --> 05:37.104
MAYBE TWICE
THIS WHOLE TIME.

05:38.805 --> 05:39.907
THAT'S NOT TRUE.

05:39.940 --> 05:41.008
[ SCOFFS ]

05:41.041 --> 05:43.977
I‐I'M OBSESSED
WITH YOUR BLACK ASS.

05:44.011 --> 05:46.713
HAVEN'T THOUGHT
OF ANYTHING ELSE FOR YEARS.

05:46.747 --> 05:48.682
[ SIGHS ]

05:51.852 --> 05:53.654
Wow.

05:55.422 --> 05:57.691
STOP!

05:57.724 --> 05:59.760
WHOLE PLACE
BOOBY‐TRAPPED.

05:59.793 --> 06:01.628
SIX WAYS TO JESUS.

06:01.662 --> 06:05.766
FOLLOW ME ‐‐ <i>EXACTLY.</i>

06:12.706 --> 06:14.741
HEYLIA...

06:14.775 --> 06:16.109
I KNOW.

06:16.143 --> 06:20.047
AND AIN'T A GODDAMN LEAF OF IT
FOR <i>YOU.</i>

06:26.053 --> 06:29.590
FUNGUS GNATS.
THEY'RE ATTRACTED TO THE POT.

06:29.623 --> 06:32.960
[ CHUCKLES ] I CAN'T BELIEVE
YOU'RE UP HERE WITH HEYLIA.

06:32.993 --> 06:36.096
ARE Y‐YOU GUYS,
LIKE, TOGETHER?

06:36.129 --> 06:37.431
COUPLE OF MONTHS AGO,

06:37.464 --> 06:40.567
SHE HAD A PROBATE ISSUE
AND HAD CONRAD CALL ME.

06:40.601 --> 06:42.035
I CAME UP.
I NEVER LEFT.

06:42.069 --> 06:44.371
LOT OF WORK FOR A POT LAWYER
UP HERE.

06:44.404 --> 06:47.574
SHE LETS ME CRASH
IN EXCHANGE FOR LEGAL HELP,

06:47.608 --> 06:48.942
BUT WE'RE JUST FRIENDS.

06:48.976 --> 06:50.177
COME ON.

06:50.210 --> 06:52.579
YOU WERE PULLING UP YOUR PANTS
WHEN YOU CAME OUT.

06:52.613 --> 06:53.647
I WAS TAKING A DUMP.

06:53.680 --> 06:56.283
SHE DOESN'T USUALLY LET ME USE
THE INSIDE TOILET.

06:56.316 --> 06:59.286
BUT SHE WAS IN A GOOD MOOD.
THANKS FOR FUCKING THAT UP.

06:59.319 --> 07:03.790
THIS WEED
IS SO FAMILIAR.

07:03.824 --> 07:06.093
HOW MANY CROPS
DOES SHE HAVE IN ROTATION?

07:06.126 --> 07:07.461
WHAT'S THE IRRIGATION?

07:07.494 --> 07:10.764
I DON'T KNOW. HEYLIA DOESN'T
LET ME UP TO THE FIELDS.

07:10.797 --> 07:14.501
LOOK AT YOU, HUH?
24?

07:14.535 --> 07:15.469
OH, SO JEALOUS.

07:15.502 --> 07:17.804
[ CHUCKLES ]
CAN I DRINK YOUR BLOOD?

07:17.838 --> 07:20.807
JUST, LIKE, A SHOT.
PLEASE?

07:20.841 --> 07:22.676
[ CHUCKLES ] NO.

07:22.709 --> 07:25.012
LIVING IN NEW YORK, HUH?

07:25.045 --> 07:26.513
I HAVEN'T
BEEN OUT MUCH YET,

07:26.547 --> 07:29.149
BUT IN DENMARK,
THINGS GOT PRETTY WILD.

07:29.183 --> 07:31.785
OH, DANISH GIRLS.

07:31.818 --> 07:34.821
YEAH.
I DATED A COUPLE.

07:34.855 --> 07:35.856
A COUPLE?

07:35.889 --> 07:36.990
WHEN I WAS YOUR AGE,

07:37.024 --> 07:38.926
I WAS SLEEPING
WITH EVERYTHING THAT MOVED.

07:38.959 --> 07:41.161
FIRST GIRL I EVER SLEPT WITH
GAVE ME CRABS.

07:41.195 --> 07:43.096
YOU EVER HAVE CRABS?
EW. NO.

07:43.130 --> 07:47.000
BY THE TIME I WAS 30,
I HAD HAD CRABS, SYPHILIS,

07:47.034 --> 07:50.070
GONORRHEA TWICE,
CHLAMYDIA THREE TIMES,

07:50.103 --> 07:54.374
LYMPHOGRANULOMA VENEREUM
IN MY URETHRA, PENILE SCABIES...

07:54.408 --> 07:57.477
AND A RECURRING BOUT
OF BACTERIAL CHANCROIDS.

07:57.511 --> 08:00.647
ONE TIME, MY FRENULUM GOT CAUGHT
ON THIS THAI CHICK'S BRACES.

08:00.681 --> 08:03.884
WE HAD TO HAVE A STREET DENTIST
IN BANGKOK SEPARATE US.

08:03.917 --> 08:06.420
I JUST SHARED A BONG
WITH YOU.

08:06.453 --> 08:08.422
YOU GOT TO REVEL
IN YOUR YOUTH, SILAS.

08:08.455 --> 08:11.225
GET CRABS EVERY ONCE IN A WHILE.
STOP BEING SUCH A PUSSY.

08:11.258 --> 08:14.261
I'M FOCUSED ON GETTING
OUR POT BUSINESS BACK UP.

08:14.294 --> 08:15.629
YOU KNOW WHAT?
NEVER MIND.

08:15.662 --> 08:17.998
I DON'T WANT TO DRINK
YOUR BLOOD. IT'S PUSSY BLOOD.

08:18.031 --> 08:19.099
LOOK WHO'S TALKING.

08:19.132 --> 08:21.101
"HEYLIA WON'T LET ME
INTO THE FIELDS."

08:21.134 --> 08:23.871
"HEYLIA WON'T LET ME
SHIT INDOORS."

08:23.904 --> 08:25.138
PUSSY.

08:25.172 --> 08:25.939
OW.

08:25.973 --> 08:27.741
BUG ON YOUR FACE.

08:29.676 --> 08:31.745
NO BUG.
JUST YOUR FACE.

08:31.778 --> 08:34.214
YOU NEED TO NUT UP.

08:35.482 --> 08:36.783
YOU'RE RIGHT.

08:36.817 --> 08:39.286
YOU'RE RIGHT.

08:41.355 --> 08:43.490
FUCK THIS.

08:43.524 --> 08:45.592
I AM GOING TO EXPLORE.

08:58.005 --> 09:02.376
THESE PLANTS
ARE <i>BEAUTIFUL.</i>

09:02.409 --> 09:03.911
WHY DO YOU THINK
THE WHOLE PLACE

09:03.944 --> 09:06.747
RIGGED LIKE
AN INDIANA JONES MOVIE?

09:06.780 --> 09:08.882
THE HYDRO.

09:08.916 --> 09:11.652
LIKE A CD ‐‐
FLAWLESS.

09:11.685 --> 09:13.687
BUT SOMETHING DEAD
ABOUT IT.

09:13.720 --> 09:17.858
THIS SHIT
IS SAM COOKE ON VINYL.

09:17.891 --> 09:19.960
THISSHIT IS ALIVE.

09:19.993 --> 09:21.962
YOU'VE CHANGED.

09:21.995 --> 09:23.230
UNH‐UNH.

09:23.263 --> 09:24.932
LEARNED.

09:24.965 --> 09:26.733
NO ONE CHANGES.

09:26.767 --> 09:28.302
WELL, <i>DEAN.</i>

09:28.335 --> 09:30.771
STEP LIGHT NOW,
SNOWFLAKE.

09:30.804 --> 09:33.340
NO, I...I GET IT.

09:33.373 --> 09:35.776
TIME MARCHES.
CHOICES NARROW.

09:35.809 --> 09:37.744
YOU GET...LONELY.

09:37.778 --> 09:38.812
SHIT.

09:38.846 --> 09:40.514
BEING LONELY'S
JUST SOMETHING

09:40.547 --> 09:43.183
INVENTED BY PEOPLE
AIN'T GOT ENOUGH WORK TO DO.

09:44.017 --> 09:45.819
SELL TO ME.

09:45.853 --> 09:47.821
NO.

09:47.855 --> 09:50.390
WOULD YOU RATHER
I ASK CONRAD?

09:50.424 --> 09:51.859
DAMN, MEMENTO.

09:51.892 --> 09:53.360
CONRAD ‐‐ I TOLD YOU.
HE'S ‐‐

09:53.393 --> 09:54.928
CONRAD LEFT
SIX MONTHS AGO.

09:54.962 --> 09:57.331
HE TOLD SILAS.

09:57.364 --> 09:58.765
CONRAD'S GONE.

10:02.369 --> 10:03.570
SO?

10:03.604 --> 10:06.273
HE TAUGHT ME.
I GOT THE LAST CROP PACKAGED.

10:06.306 --> 10:07.708
THIS ONE'S
READY TO HARVEST.

10:07.741 --> 10:10.677
HAVE TO HIRE A BUNCH
OF STINK‐ASS HIPPIES TO HELP,

10:10.711 --> 10:13.313
BUT I'LL MANAGE ‐‐
ALWAYS DO.

10:14.748 --> 10:17.284
LOOK,
I'M SORRY YOU'RE ALONE.

10:17.317 --> 10:21.855
DON'T <i>YOU</i> FEEL SORRY
FOR <i>ME.</i>

10:21.889 --> 10:23.991
ESPECIALLY WHEN
THIS SHIT'S YOUR FAULT.

10:24.024 --> 10:25.592
MY FAULT?

10:25.626 --> 10:30.864
MY KITCHEN TABLE WAS FULL
EVERY NIGHT ‐‐ EVERY NIGHT ‐‐

10:30.898 --> 10:32.833
'FORE YOU WANDERED
INTO MY LIFE.

10:32.866 --> 10:34.801
MEANWHILE,
YOU OUT OF PRISON ONE DAY,

10:34.835 --> 10:36.904
AND YOUR WHOLE FAMILY
COME RUNNING.

10:36.937 --> 10:39.239
I...DIDN'T ASK THEM TO.

10:39.273 --> 10:41.575
THEN WALK AWAY.
LET 'EM GO.

10:41.608 --> 10:42.509
YOUR STORY DON'T END WELL,

10:42.543 --> 10:44.811
AND IF THEY DON'T KNOW THAT
BY NOW,

10:44.845 --> 10:46.113
THEY AS STUPID
AS YOU ARE.

10:46.146 --> 10:47.714
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

10:47.748 --> 10:49.616
FUCK YOU, HEYLIA.

10:50.851 --> 10:55.722
ON MY PROPERTY, ON MY TIME ‐‐
FUCK ME?

10:55.756 --> 10:58.192
FUCK YOU!

10:58.225 --> 11:01.895
IT'S NOT THAT SIMPLE
JUST TO WALK AWAY.

11:01.929 --> 11:04.798
WALKING AWAY IS SIMPLE
AS SUGAR COOKIES, BABY.

11:04.831 --> 11:06.733
WATCH.

11:06.767 --> 11:07.968
[ SIGHS ]

11:08.001 --> 11:10.170
HEYLIA?

11:11.538 --> 11:13.574
SHIT.

11:13.607 --> 11:15.375
HEYLIA?

11:15.409 --> 11:16.476
HEYLIA?

11:16.510 --> 11:18.212
WE'RE SUPPOSED TO HAVE
A GUEST SPEAKER,

11:18.245 --> 11:20.614
BUT HE SEEMS TO BE LATE.

11:20.647 --> 11:23.984
ANY QUESTIONS
FROM LAST WEEK?

11:24.918 --> 11:26.687
HOW ACCURATE
IS "THE WIRE"?

11:26.720 --> 11:28.889
[ DOOR OPENS, STUDENTS MURMUR ]

11:28.922 --> 11:32.326
HERE.
SIT DOWN, YOU SHITHEAD.

11:32.359 --> 11:34.361
AND STAY THERE,
OR I'LL PUNCH YOU

11:34.394 --> 11:36.697
RIGHT IN
YOUR UGLY FUCKIN' FACE!

11:36.730 --> 11:37.931
ALL RIGHT, ALL RIGHT.
DAMN, MAN.

11:37.965 --> 11:39.199
I'M SORRY, PROFESSOR.

11:39.233 --> 11:40.701
I WAS DRIVING HERE,

11:40.734 --> 11:44.304
AND I SAW THIS SCUMBAG I LIKE
FOR A RAPE IN MORNINGSIDE PARK.

11:44.338 --> 11:46.740
BUT HE WON'T BE A PROBLEM,
OR I'LL SHOOT HIM IN THE KIDNEY.

11:46.773 --> 11:47.808
RIGHT, FUCKSTAIN?!

11:47.841 --> 11:49.843
YEAH. YEAH.

11:49.877 --> 11:51.879
NAME'S DETECTIVE OUELLETTE.

11:51.912 --> 11:53.247
25th PRECINCT.

11:53.280 --> 11:56.517
I AM A PAWN
FOR POLITICAL ELECTIONS.

11:56.550 --> 11:59.419
