WHATEVER WE WANT?

12:20.507 --> 12:22.342
RELIGION?

12:22.376 --> 12:23.510
FAILED.

12:23.544 --> 12:25.479
PARENTING?

12:25.512 --> 12:26.914
IT'S EXTINCT.

12:26.947 --> 12:29.883
IT'S BECAUSE OF <i>THIS.</i>

12:29.917 --> 12:33.587
THE NEW YORK PENAL LAW BOOK.

12:33.620 --> 12:34.755
[ THUD ]

12:34.788 --> 12:35.722
AND THIS.

12:35.756 --> 12:36.890
[ STUDENTS GASP ]

12:36.924 --> 12:39.993
A 9‐MILLIMETER SIG P226.

12:40.027 --> 12:41.762
HAVE YOU SEEN
"THE WIRE"?

12:41.795 --> 12:43.330
FUCK YOU.

12:43.363 --> 12:46.500
ALL RIGHT, I'M GONNA OUTLINE
A COUPLE OF CASES HERE

12:46.533 --> 12:47.334
THAT ARE VERY RECENT.

12:47.367 --> 12:48.735
WHY ARE YOU
BULLSHITTING US?

12:51.305 --> 12:53.707
