WOULD YOU BE REFERRING?

12:55.776 --> 12:58.712
YO, GET THE FUCK OFF ME!
WHAT ‐‐

12:58.745 --> 13:00.047
HE'S NOT
A RAPE SUSPECT.

13:00.080 --> 13:03.817
OR YOU DON'T BELIEVE
IN PATTING DOWN YOUR PERPS.

13:03.851 --> 13:05.853
