IS ACTUALLY MY PARTNER,

13:14.862 --> 13:16.997
DETECTIVE TYSON BETZ.

13:17.030 --> 13:18.866
MEET ‐‐
UH, WHAT'S YOUR NAME?

13:18.899 --> 13:20.234
SHANE BOTWIN.

13:20.267 --> 13:24.371
THE ONLY KID IN HERE WHO'S
PAYING ATTENTION TO DETAILS.

13:24.404 --> 13:25.839
CONGRATULATIONS.

13:25.873 --> 13:27.841
I'M GONNA GO SMOKE.

13:27.875 --> 13:30.711
GET OUT OF
THESE STUPID‐ASS CLOTHES.

13:30.744 --> 13:32.513
NICE JOB, BOTWIN.

13:32.546 --> 13:35.015
NOW SIT DOWN AND SHUT UP.

13:35.048 --> 13:37.518
THREE CASES.
LET'S SEE WHAT WE GOT.

13:37.551 --> 13:39.887
HEYLIA?

13:39.920 --> 13:42.422
HEYLIA?

13:50.764 --> 13:52.766
[ FROG CROAKS ]

13:59.740 --> 14:01.675
[ SIGHS ]

14:14.555 --> 14:16.690
[ CLICK ]

14:33.674 --> 14:37.744
GET YOUR ASS OFF MY COUNTER.
THIS AIN'T "FAMILY TIES."

14:39.947 --> 14:42.282
WHY DID CONRAD LEAVE?

14:43.851 --> 14:45.986
FOOL MET
THIS LITTLE CHINESE GIRL ‐‐

14:46.019 --> 14:48.589
ECON, PhD.

14:48.622 --> 14:50.657
ASIANS AND THEIR NUMBERS.

14:50.691 --> 14:53.627
TO GO ON AND RUN DOWN TO L. A.,
SELL TO THE CLUBS.

14:53.660 --> 14:57.698
SPENT THE WHOLE TIME TELLING HIM
HE DESERVED A BIGGER CUT.

14:57.731 --> 14:59.900
CAME HOME,
SAID, "I WANT MORE."

14:59.933 --> 15:01.535
I TOLD HIM,
"A," "FUCK YOU,"

15:01.568 --> 15:04.238
AND "B,"
"YOU BEST STOP SEEING HER."

15:04.271 --> 15:06.173
TWO DAYS LATER, HE'S GONE.

15:09.142 --> 15:11.311
I KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE GROWING, HEYLIA.

15:12.880 --> 15:14.014
IT'S MILF.

15:14.047 --> 15:15.749
YOU'RE GROWING MILF.

15:15.782 --> 15:17.818
I THOUGHT
IT WAS LOST FOREVER.

15:17.851 --> 15:19.786
DIDN'T YOUR LITTLE FANCY
PRIVATE SCHOOL

15:19.820 --> 15:21.755
TELL YOU
NOTHING GETS LOST?

15:21.788 --> 15:24.992
JUST SHOWS UP
IN A DIFFERENT FORM.

15:25.025 --> 15:26.827
MAYBE
WITH A NEW HAIR COLOR.

15:26.860 --> 15:30.063
OR MAYBE
TRYING TO STEAL FROM ME.

15:30.097 --> 15:31.565
IN OTHER WORDS,

15:31.598 --> 15:34.434
GIVE ME THE FUCKING SEEDS
YOU TOOK OUT OF THAT DRAWER.

15:34.468 --> 15:36.470
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

15:37.971 --> 15:40.073
THIS IS MY STRAIN.

15:41.108 --> 15:43.610
BITCH,
CONRAD INVENTED MILF

15:43.644 --> 15:47.080
WHEN YOU WERE STILL SELLING
DIME BAGS FOR YOUR MOMMY.

15:47.114 --> 15:50.817
OUT OF YOUR GODDAMN MIND,
TRYING TO STEAL FROM ME.

15:50.851 --> 15:51.852
FINE.

15:51.885 --> 15:54.988
BUT WE CREATED MILF 2.0
TOGETHER.

15:55.022 --> 15:57.090
JUST BECAUSE
YOU DROVE CONRAD AWAY

15:57.124 --> 15:58.759
DOESN'T MEAN
IT'S YOURS NOW.

16:00.160 --> 16:01.495
HOW OLD ARE YOU?

16:01.528 --> 16:04.298
24.

16:04.331 --> 16:05.165
OKAY.

16:05.199 --> 16:06.733
SO NANCY'S STILL GOT
A GOOD 10 YEARS

16:06.767 --> 16:10.370
OF YOU FOLLOWING HER AROUND,
SLINGING HER DIME BAGS.

16:10.404 --> 16:11.705
WE'RE PARTNERS.

16:11.738 --> 16:14.975
OH, CONRAD
USED TO SAY THAT, TOO.

16:15.008 --> 16:17.644
IT'S PRETTY BIG OF YOU
TO WORK FOR HER

16:17.678 --> 16:20.514
AFTER FINDING OUT
YOUR DADDY AIN'T YOUR DADDY.

16:21.915 --> 16:25.018
OH, CONRAD'S A GOSSIP.

16:26.753 --> 16:28.589
THAT'S NONE
OF YOUR BUSINESS.

16:33.093 --> 16:35.863
BOY,
DON'T YOU SLAM MY DOOR.

16:35.896 --> 16:36.864
[ DOOR SLAMS ]

16:36.897 --> 16:41.134
WELL, THANKS
FOR LETTING ME COME ‐‐

16:41.168 --> 16:43.403
JUST BEGIN? OKAY.

16:43.437 --> 16:47.341
GENTLEMEN, ALLOW ME TO INTRODUCE
THE COPENHAGEN WHEEL,

16:47.374 --> 16:51.245
A REVOLUTIONARY ACCESSORY
THAT TURNS YOUR BICYCLE

16:51.278 --> 16:53.080
INTO AN ELECTRIC HYBRID,

16:53.113 --> 16:55.849
STORING THE ENERGY
YOU EXPEND PEDALING

16:55.883 --> 16:58.085
TO GIVE YOU A BOOST
WHEN YOU NEED IT.

16:59.920 --> 17:01.188
[ SNIFFS ]

17:01.221 --> 17:02.923
HOW ABOUT ‐‐ HOW ABOUT I, UH,
SHOW A SALES VIDEO?

17:02.956 --> 17:06.693
KEEP IN MIND, I MADE
THIS FOR A SLIGHTLY
DIFFERENT AUDIENCE, SO...

17:06.727 --> 17:07.861
[ CLICKS TONGUE ]

17:07.895 --> 17:09.062
OH.

17:09.096 --> 17:10.564
<i>GOOD DAY.</i>

17:10.597 --> 17:13.567
<i>I'M LOCAL MICRO‐CELEBRITY</i>
<i>AND DANMARKS</i>

17:13.600 --> 17:17.604
NATIONALSOCIALISTISKE
BEVAEGELSE MAYORAL CANDIDATE

17:17.638 --> 17:18.605
<i>"FUN‐BIKE" ANDY.</i>

17:18.639 --> 17:21.241
<i>I'M HERE TALKING</i>
<i>TO COPENHAGEN RESIDENTS</i>

17:21.275 --> 17:23.243
<i>ABOUT A MIRACULOUS</i>
<i>NEW INVENTION.</i>

17:23.277 --> 17:26.213
<i>EXCUSE ME, SIR,</i>
<i>WHAT WOULD YOU SAY</i>

17:26.246 --> 17:28.849
<i>IS THE TOUGHEST PART</i>
<i>ABOUT LIFE IN COPENHAGEN?</i>

17:28.882 --> 17:30.217
<i>THE MUSLIMS.</i>

17:30.250 --> 17:31.885
[ <i>CHUCKLES</i>]
<i>I'M KIDDING. KIDDING.</i>

17:31.919 --> 17:33.554
<i>NO, THE COMMUTE,</i>
<i>FOR SURE.</i>

17:33.587 --> 17:36.690
<i>BIKING UP THESE HILLS</i>
<i>LEAVES ME ZEER POOPED.</i>

17:36.723 --> 17:39.459
<i>WELL, TRY THIS.</i>

17:39.493 --> 17:40.827
[ <i>TWINKLE!</i>]

17:40.861 --> 17:43.530
<i>WOW!</i>

17:43.564 --> 17:45.165
<i>THANK YOU, STRANGER!</i>

17:45.199 --> 17:46.667
<i>CELEBRITIES LOVE IT,</i>
<i>TOO.</i>

17:46.700 --> 17:49.403
I USE THE COPENHAGEN WHEEL
<i>FOR TRANSPORT TO THE SET</i>

17:49.436 --> 17:51.805
<i>OF MY HIT</i>
<i>TELEVISION DRAMA PROGRAM,</i>

17:51.839 --> 17:53.540
"CRIME ROBBERY POLICEFORCE."

17:53.574 --> 17:56.677
I AM BUT A SIMPLE PUPPETEER,
AND EVENI <i>CAN AFFORD ONE.</i>

17:56.710 --> 17:58.745
<i>YEAH,</i>
<i>AND IT WILL BE PERFECT</i>

17:58.779 --> 18:01.048
FOR WHEN WE START A FAMILY
<i>VERY SOON.</i>

18:01.081 --> 18:04.718
Silas: <i>THE COPENHAGEN WHEEL</i>
<i>MAKES ME JUMP FOR ‐‐</i>

18:04.751 --> 18:07.287
<i>I THINK</i>
<i>I TWISTED MY ANKLE.</i>

18:07.321 --> 18:10.991
AND THE COPENHAGEN WHEEL
IS SURPRISINGLY INEXPENSIVE.

18:11.024 --> 18:12.659
<i>AND WITH THE TAX CREDITS</i>

18:12.693 --> 18:14.361
<i>FROM THE RECENT REPEAL</i>
<i>OF THE HERRING TARIFF,</i>

18:14.394 --> 18:17.865
THE COPENHAGEN WHEEL
IS EVEN MORE AFFORDABLE STILL!

18:17.898 --> 18:19.700
[ REMOTE CLICKS ]

18:19.733 --> 18:22.102
YOU GUYS RECOGNIZE DOUG?

18:22.135 --> 18:23.871
UH, HOW MUCH
ARE YOU LOOKING FOR HERE?

18:23.904 --> 18:27.774
UM...75, 80.

18:27.808 --> 18:29.109
80 MIL
FOR A BIKE ACCESSORY?

18:29.142 --> 18:31.979
NO. NO, NO, NO.
$80,000. YEAH.

18:32.012 --> 18:33.881
$90,000
IF I REDO THE FLOORS.

18:33.914 --> 18:35.949
I HAVE A GREAT RETAIL SPACE
IN P. A. M. P. A.

18:35.983 --> 18:38.018
DO YOU KNOW THE ‐‐
THE PARALLELOGRAM

18:38.051 --> 18:40.087
ABOVE THE MANHATTAN
PSYCHIATRIC ASYLUM?

18:40.120 --> 18:42.589
IT'S A REAL UP‐AND‐COMING
NEIGHBORHOOD, SO...

18:42.623 --> 18:43.757
[ LAUGHS ]

18:43.790 --> 18:45.859
THANK YOU,
MR. BOTWIN.

18:45.893 --> 18:47.294
SO, ARE YOU
GONNA FUND ME?

18:47.327 --> 18:50.030
COME BACK WHEN YOUR MARKET CAP
IS CLOSER TO...

18:50.063 --> 18:51.598
UH...
[ CHUCKLES ]

18:51.632 --> 18:54.835
WHEN YOU HAVE
A MARKET CAP.

18:54.868 --> 18:55.936
[ LAUGHTER ]

18:55.969 --> 18:58.138
THANK YOU
FOR COMING BY.

18:58.172 --> 18:59.573
THANKS FOR YOUR TIME.

18:59.606 --> 19:02.609
YOU LOOKED GOOD,
ROCKET MAN.
YEAH.
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

19:08.982 --> 19:11.718
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

19:11.752 --> 19:13.420
EXCUSE ME, DETECTIVE?

19:13.453 --> 19:17.090
OH, ENCYCLOPEDIA FUCKIN' BROWN.
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

19:17.124 --> 19:18.292
YOU TALKED ABOUT THE CASE

19:18.325 --> 19:20.294
WITH THE MAILBOX PLACE
THAT GOT SHOT UP.

19:20.327 --> 19:23.297
YOU SAID IT WAS A FRONT,
LIKE A FAKE STORE?

19:23.330 --> 19:24.598
NO,
IT WAS A REAL SHOP ‐‐

19:24.631 --> 19:26.967
LEGITIMATE BUSINESS
COVERING AN ILLEGAL ONE ‐‐

19:27.000 --> 19:28.735
PROSTITUTION,
IN THIS CASE.

19:28.769 --> 19:30.637
COVERING HOW?
LIKE ON PAPER?

19:30.671 --> 19:32.105
YEAH.
AND FOOT TRAFFIC.

19:32.139 --> 19:33.507
THEY DIDN'T RAISE SUSPICION

19:33.540 --> 19:35.309
WITH ALL THOSE MOPES WALKING
IN AND OUT OF THERE ALL DAY,

19:35.342 --> 19:36.810
CHECKING THEIR MAIL,
RIGHT.

19:36.844 --> 19:38.745
DID THEY LAUNDER
THE MONEY, TOO?

19:39.913 --> 19:41.148
ARE YOU TAKING THIS CLASS

19:41.181 --> 19:43.817
BECAUSE "THE FILMS OF NIC CAGE"
WAS ALL FILLED UP,

19:43.851 --> 19:45.485
OR ARE YOU
REALLY INTERESTED?

19:45.519 --> 19:46.720
NO, I'M TOTALLY INTO IT.

19:46.753 --> 19:48.755
ALL RIGHT.
YOU TAKE MY CARD.

19:48.789 --> 19:51.692
IF YOU WANT TO COME DOWN
TO THE PRECINCT SOMETIME,

19:51.725 --> 19:52.793
I'LL SHOW YOU AROUND.

19:52.826 --> 19:54.394
THAT ‐‐
THAT SOUNDS FRUITY.

19:54.428 --> 19:55.796
WHAT I MEAN IS

19:55.829 --> 19:57.598
THE POLICE ACADEMY
ISN'T EXACTLY BURSTING

19:57.631 --> 19:59.766
WITH THE BRAIN TRUST
OF YOUR GENERATION,

19:59.800 --> 20:01.401
IF YOU KNOW
WHAT I'M SAYING.

20:01.435 --> 20:02.836
OKAY.

20:02.870 --> 20:04.338
LATER, BOTWIN.

20:04.371 --> 20:05.639
SEE YOU AROUND.

20:12.212 --> 20:14.348
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACH ]

20:15.849 --> 20:17.384
WAIT, SILAS! STOP!

20:17.417 --> 20:20.087
WHAT?

20:20.120 --> 20:22.556
[ SIGHS ]
NOTHING.

20:22.589 --> 20:24.758
YOU KNOW THIS IS MILF?

20:24.791 --> 20:26.093
REALLY?

20:26.126 --> 20:28.228
I THOUGHT
MILF WAS LOST.

20:28.262 --> 20:30.697
NOTHING'S EVER LOST.

20:30.731 --> 20:32.966
UH, I WAS THINKING

20:33.000 --> 20:35.636
WE'D SHOW HEYLIA THE MONEY,
ARRANGE TRANSPORT,

20:35.669 --> 20:38.038
EXPLAIN TO HER WHY HAVING
HER PRODUCT IN NEW YORK ‐‐

20:38.071 --> 20:39.640
WE HAVEN'T TALKED YET,
YOU KNOW.

20:39.673 --> 20:42.009
I TRY, BUT YOU KEEP STALLING,
SO WE'RE GONNA DO IT NOW.

20:43.043 --> 20:44.344
TALK ABOUT WHAT?

20:44.378 --> 20:47.548
WHAT DID HE SAY
WHEN I WAS BORN, HUH?

20:47.581 --> 20:52.286
"WELL, DOESN'T LOOK LIKE ME.
THAT'S WEIRD.

20:52.319 --> 20:53.420
OH, WELL."

20:53.453 --> 20:55.355
DIDN'T MATTER TO HIM.

20:55.389 --> 20:56.690
BULLSHIT.

20:56.723 --> 20:59.426
OR IS YOUR MEMORY
JUST AS SCREWED UP
AS EVERYTHING ELSE?

21:01.128 --> 21:04.865
YOU WERE BORN
AT 10:59 A. M.

21:04.898 --> 21:06.567
THE WALLS OF MY ROOM
WERE PINK

21:06.600 --> 21:09.536
WITH A FADED BORDER
OF QUARTER HORSES ALONG THE TOP.

21:09.570 --> 21:13.640
A NURSE WAS PLAYING "SUNSHINE
OF YOUR LOVE" AS YOU EMERGED.

21:13.674 --> 21:16.343
MY FIRST THOUGHT WAS
I WANTED TO EAT ONE OF YOUR TOES

21:16.376 --> 21:18.612
SO I COULD STILL KEEP
A PIECE OF YOU INSIDE OF ME.

21:18.645 --> 21:19.746
MY SECOND THOUGHT WAS,

21:19.780 --> 21:22.816
"IF JUDAH DOES NOT LOVE
THIS BABY, I'M GONNA LEAVE HIM."

21:22.850 --> 21:26.053
SO YOU SEE?
MY MEMORY IS PERFECT.

21:26.086 --> 21:29.923
EVERYTHING YOU SAY, MOM,
JUST SOUNDS LIKE STUFF TO SAY.

21:29.957 --> 21:31.225
IT DOESN'T ACTUALLY
MEAN ANYTHING.

21:31.258 --> 21:33.460
DOES IT REALLY MATTER
IN THE END?

21:33.493 --> 21:35.829
DOES HE SHOW UP ANY LESS
IN YOUR DREAMS?

21:35.863 --> 21:37.464
DOES HE MEAN ANY LESS
TO YOU?

21:38.532 --> 21:39.867
NO.

21:39.900 --> 21:41.201
YOU DO.

21:45.739 --> 21:49.042
PART OF HIM KNEW, I THINK,
WHETHER I TOLD HIM OR NOT.

21:49.076 --> 21:51.912
AND H‐HE HAD ROOM
IN HIS HEART.

21:51.945 --> 21:53.447
YOU WERE HIS.

21:53.480 --> 21:55.148
YOU NEVER TOLD HIM?

21:57.751 --> 22:02.422
THAT IS SO UNBELIEVABLY
DECEITFUL.

22:02.456 --> 22:03.524
I DID IT FOR YOU.

22:03.557 --> 22:05.993
YOU DON'T GET TO MAKE
THOSE CHOICES FOR OTHER PEOPLE.

22:06.026 --> 22:08.562
YOU WOULD HAVE PREFERRED WHAT,
THAT I ABORT YOU?!

22:08.595 --> 22:09.530
AND YOU DON'T GET CREDIT

22:09.563 --> 22:12.833
FOR HAVING A BABY
WITH FUCKING LARS.

22:12.866 --> 22:15.702
HE'S SO DUMB!
I‐I GOT THE DUMB GENES!

22:15.736 --> 22:16.803
YOU'RE NOT DUMB.

22:16.837 --> 22:18.472
YEAH,
SHANE GOT OTHER THINGS,

22:18.505 --> 22:21.642
BUT YOU'RE SWEET
AND SO GOOD‐LOOKING

22:21.675 --> 22:25.112
AND NOT A MURDERER, WHICH
PUTS YOU SQUARELY IN THE LEAD.

22:25.145 --> 22:28.315
SO, YEAH, I KEPT YOU IN THE DARK
FOR MUCH OF YOUR LIFE,

22:28.348 --> 22:31.185
BUT YOU GAVE ME STRETCH MARKS,
SO WE'RE EVEN.

22:32.719 --> 22:34.121
DAD'S DEAD.

22:34.154 --> 22:35.522
YOU LIED TO ME
MY WHOLE LIFE,

22:35.556 --> 22:38.025
AND I'M STUCK HERE WITH YOU
FUCKING ENDLESSLY.

22:38.058 --> 22:41.628
SO NO, MOM,
WE'RE NOT EVEN CLOSE TO EVEN.

22:45.365 --> 22:47.801
I DID IT!
I FOUND YOU GUYS!

22:47.835 --> 22:49.803
FUCK YOU, HEYLIA!
DEAN HODES IS A MAN!

22:49.837 --> 22:50.838
[ SNAP ]

22:50.871 --> 22:53.307
FUCK!

22:53.340 --> 22:55.542
[ SCREAMING ]

22:55.576 --> 22:57.177
OH, GOD!

22:57.211 --> 22:59.179
NOW, THIS PLACE
IS STILL CONFIGURED

22:59.213 --> 23:00.380
FOR THE LAST BUSINESS,

23:00.414 --> 23:02.749
BUT I'M CONFIDENT
YOU'LL SEE THE POTENTIAL.

23:02.783 --> 23:03.884
[ CHUCKLES ]

23:03.917 --> 23:05.485
MY FIRST GAY BAR.

23:05.519 --> 23:07.888
THE REAL‐ESTATE LADY
PROMISED SHE WOULD
HAVE THIS CLEANED UP.

23:07.921 --> 23:09.556
WHAT'S BACK HERE?

23:09.590 --> 23:11.058
UH...

23:11.091 --> 23:14.862
KITCHEN,
EMPLOYEE‐CHANGING AREA, DUNGEON.

23:14.895 --> 23:16.897
IS THERE A BACK DOOR?

23:16.930 --> 23:18.432
YEAH ‐‐
GOES OUT TO AN ALLEY.

23:18.465 --> 23:20.901
GREAT.
IT'S PERFECT.

23:20.934 --> 23:22.803
YOU MEAN ‐‐

23:22.836 --> 23:24.538
I'LL FRONT YOU
THE START‐UP MONEY.

23:24.571 --> 23:26.440
JUST LIKE THAT?

23:26.473 --> 23:29.643
OH, MY GOD! SHANE!

23:29.676 --> 23:31.211
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

23:31.245 --> 23:33.780
YOU HAVE NO IDEA HOW MUCH
IT MEANS THAT YOU BELIEVE IN ME.

23:33.814 --> 23:34.781
I DON'T BELIEVE IN YOU.

23:34.815 --> 23:36.517
YOU HAVE
NO BUSINESS PLAN.

23:36.550 --> 23:38.652
THIS IS A TERRIBLE LOCATION
FOR FOOT TRAFFIC.

23:38.685 --> 23:41.054
AND YOU DON'T EVEN KNOW
IF THE COPENHAGEN WHEEL

23:41.088 --> 23:43.023
IS STREET‐LEGAL
IN THE UNITED STATES YET.

23:43.056 --> 23:44.791
T‐THEN WHY
ARE YOU INVESTING?

23:44.825 --> 23:46.093
AS A FRONT FOR MOM.

23:46.126 --> 23:48.595
SHE THINKS SHE NEEDS SILAS,
BUT SHE NEEDS <i>ME.</i>

23:48.629 --> 23:50.430
NO WAY.

23:50.464 --> 23:53.300
THIS IS GONNA BE
A LEGITIMATE RETAIL BUSINESS.

23:53.333 --> 23:55.802
IT WILL BE.
THE MAIN SPACE IS ALL YOURS.

23:55.836 --> 23:57.137
DRUG STUFF IN THE BACK.

23:57.171 --> 24:00.174
WE'LL USE THE ALLEY FOR
DELIVERIES. COMPLETELY HIDDEN.

24:03.076 --> 24:05.045
THIS ISN'T
WHAT I WANTED.

24:05.078 --> 24:06.613
JUST THINK OF IT
LIKE IN "GOODFELLAS"

24:06.647 --> 24:09.149
WHEN THAT GUY COMES TO PAULIE
FOR HELP AT THE RESTAURANT.

24:09.183 --> 24:12.152
PAULIE USED THE RESTAURANT
AS A CRIMINAL HUB.

24:12.186 --> 24:15.122
THEN HE TORCHED THE PLACE
ONCE HE SUCKED IT DRY.

24:17.691 --> 24:19.760
WHAT'S YOUR POINT?

24:21.929 --> 24:22.996
HOW IS HE?

24:23.030 --> 24:24.464
HE'LL SLEEP
TILL THE DOCTOR GETS HERE.

24:24.498 --> 24:27.935
TOLD THAT IDIOT
TO NEVER GO OUT THERE.

24:27.968 --> 24:29.770
HEYLIA...

24:29.803 --> 24:32.105
PEOPLE LOVE MILF.

24:32.139 --> 24:33.607
THEY DON'T HAVE IT
IN NEW YORK YET.

24:33.640 --> 24:36.877
WE CAN OPEN UP THAT MARKET.
WE HAVE CUSTOMERS.

24:36.910 --> 24:38.946
YOU HAVE A PACKAGE
READY TO GO.

24:38.979 --> 24:40.247
WE CAN BUY RIGHT NOW,

24:40.280 --> 24:42.883
AND YOU DON'T
HAVE TO DRIVE ANYWHERE ‐‐

24:42.916 --> 24:44.484
STOP.

24:44.518 --> 24:46.119
I'LL SUPPLY YOU.

24:46.920 --> 24:48.555
ON ONE CONDITION.

24:48.589 --> 24:50.390
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

24:50.424 --> 24:52.826
GREAT. THANK YOU.

24:52.860 --> 24:53.927
WHAT IS IT?

24:53.961 --> 24:55.462
GIVE ME SILAS.

24:55.495 --> 24:56.463
WHAT?

24:56.496 --> 24:57.631
WHAT?

24:57.664 --> 24:58.899
NOT PERMANENTLY.

24:58.932 --> 25:00.767
HE HELPS HARVEST
THE CURRENT CROP,

25:00.801 --> 25:02.936
THEN HE GETS
WHAT'S ALREADY PACKAGED,

25:02.970 --> 25:05.906
RENTS A VEHICLE, TRANSPORTS IT
TO NEW YORK HIMSELF.

25:05.939 --> 25:07.908
OFFER'S ON THE TABLE ‐‐
FIVE MINUTES.

25:07.941 --> 25:10.711
WELL, THIS IS STUPID.
LET'S GO.

25:10.744 --> 25:11.778
I'LL DO IT.

25:11.812 --> 25:14.047
FUCK NO.
YOU CAN'T HAVE MY SON.

25:14.081 --> 25:15.382
SURE SHE CAN.

25:15.415 --> 25:17.251
WE NEED THIS.

25:17.284 --> 25:18.352
I'LL STAY.

25:18.385 --> 25:21.555
I D‐‐ I MEAN...

25:21.588 --> 25:22.689
ARE YOU SURE?

25:24.791 --> 25:27.928
OKAY, THEN. FINE.

25:27.961 --> 25:29.630
UM...

25:29.663 --> 25:32.866
YOU KNOW I'M DOING THIS ‐‐
I'M DOING ALL THIS FOR MY CHILD.

25:32.900 --> 25:33.934
I'M NOT A CHILD.

25:33.967 --> 25:35.435
I MEANT STEVIE.

25:35.469 --> 25:36.603
[ CHUCKLES ]

25:36.637 --> 25:38.038
NO.

25:38.071 --> 25:40.073
Y‐YOU'RE MY CHILD, TOO.

25:41.909 --> 25:43.810
SO...
I GET IT, THOUGH.

25:43.844 --> 25:46.013
UM, I'LL SEE YOU
IN NEW YORK.

25:46.046 --> 25:48.916
DRIVE SAFE, OKAY?
BE SAFE.

25:48.949 --> 25:51.518
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

25:51.552 --> 25:53.086
SIT.

25:53.120 --> 25:56.223
FIX YOU SOMETHING TO EAT
BEFORE YOU GET STARTED.

26:00.227 --> 26:02.529
IT'S A HORRIBLE MISTAKE.

26:02.563 --> 26:04.164
AND THE BOTTOM LINE IS,

26:04.198 --> 26:07.868
I SHOULD NOT BE EVER LET LOOSE
IN SAN FRANCISCO.

26:07.901 --> 26:10.270
WHAT ABOUT YOU?

26:10.304 --> 26:13.607
ASIDE FROM LOSING SILAS
TO HIS FRIENDS FOR THE WEEKEND,

26:13.640 --> 26:14.808
YOU STAY OUT OF TROUBLE?

26:14.842 --> 26:16.743
I WAS A GOOD GIRL.

26:16.777 --> 26:18.846
GOOD GIRL.

26:18.879 --> 26:20.080
[ GROANS ]

26:20.113 --> 26:22.883
I HAVE TO REST MY EYES,
I THINK.

26:22.916 --> 26:24.284
UM...

26:24.318 --> 26:27.888
TELL ME SOMETHING INTERESTING
FOR MY BOOK.

26:27.921 --> 26:31.625
THAT WOULD BE
A NICE THING TO DO.

26:31.658 --> 26:32.926
OKAY.

26:32.960 --> 26:35.462
UM...

26:35.495 --> 26:37.831
I ALMOST STEPPED
IN A BEAR TRAP TODAY.

26:37.865 --> 26:39.867
MM‐HMM.

26:39.900 --> 26:41.735
[ CHUCKLES SOFTLY ]

26:41.768 --> 26:44.972
ALSO...

26:45.005 --> 26:46.507
SOMEONE ACCUSED ME

26:46.540 --> 26:52.246
OF ONLY BEING AWARE
OF WHAT'S RIGHT IN FRONT OF ME.

26:52.279 --> 26:55.782
I DIDN'T DEFEND MYSELF,
BUT IT ISN'T TRUE.

26:55.816 --> 26:58.318
THE OPPOSITE.

26:58.352 --> 27:02.523
ANY MOMENT ‐‐
EATING LUNCH, WASHING MY HAIR ‐‐

27:02.556 --> 27:08.896
I'M AWARE OF ALL MY PEOPLE,
WHEREVER THEY ARE.

27:08.929 --> 27:11.999
AND I CARRY THEM, YOU KNOW.

27:12.032 --> 27:18.272
OTHERWISE,
THEY MIGHT...SLIP AWAY.

27:18.305 --> 27:19.673
AND THEN WHAT?

27:21.375 --> 27:23.177
HEY.

27:56.910 --> 27:58.045
WHAT THE FUCK?

27:58.078 --> 28:01.648
THAT'S NOT EVEN A STORY.
IT'S NOT A STORY.

28:02.850 --> 28:04.785
Sorry.

28:04.818 --> 28:05.986
[ GROANS ]

28:06.019 --> 28:09.223
I'll have some better ones
for you next time.

28:09.256 --> 28:10.991
MM‐HMM.

